data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Situated on a CONSERVATION LOT, 4046 Creswick Cir offers not just a home but a lifestyle. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior that seamlessly combines modern elegance with practical functionality. The open-concept living space features a harmonious Living Room/Dining Room Combo. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with all new 2019 black stainless steel appliances and LED lighting above the 42" cabinets. The lower kitchen cabinets include slide out trays so you don't have to bend over to see what is in the back of your cabinet. Just slide a shelf out and you can access even the furthest back items! The eating space in the kitchen offers a cozy spot for family meals, and the granite counters add a touch of sophistication to the space. The primary bedroom, conveniently located on the main floor, offers a retreat-like ambiance with a walk-in closet offering custom built-in cabinets. Enjoy working from home in the office located in the front of the house for privacy. This home is wired for fiber optic internet as well so you'll always have a seamless connection. The remaining four bedrooms, all located upstairs, provide flexibility for a growing family or guests. An additional closet has been added at the top of the stairs for even more storage! The upstairs full bathroom also offers a double vanity sink so that mornings and evenings are simplified, ensuring everyone's comfort and privacy. The attached garage, with space for two vehicles, offers ceiling storage racks, which adds convenience and security to your daily routine. Enjoy a nice cup of morning coffee on your brick paver lanai while you watch the wild deer and hawks who frequent your backyard. The white vinyl fence belongs to this property! ADDITIONAL FEATURES include: freshly painted interior 2023, granite throughout kitchen and bathrooms, all bedroom closets are French doors, surround sound inside and outside, upgraded Dan's fans in primary bedroom and living room with a lifetime warranty, 3 exterior Eufy security cameras and video doorbell, 2 nest thermostats, gutters, vinyl fence, screened front door enclosure, and concrete edging/borders around flower beds. Enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities, Lake Nona YMCA (8 miles), South Econ Community Park (3 miles) and Young Pine Community Park (1 mile). Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your home sweet home!
